There are some features that make it into some bindings before others.  Just starting
to keep a list here so that they're tracked and can be completed later.

|=======================================================|======|=====|========|======|
| Feature                                               | Ruby | PHP | Python | Java |
|=======================================================|======|=====|========|======|
| Passing optional parameters to related / recommended  | x    | x   |        |      |
|-------------------------------------------------------|------|-----|--------|------|
| Batch related (for multiple items)                    |      | x   |        |      |
|-------------------------------------------------------|------|-----|--------|------|
| Group / basket recommendations                        | x    | x   |        |      |
|-------------------------------------------------------|------|-----|--------|------|
| Link-type support                                     |      | x   | x      |      |
|-------------------------------------------------------|------|-----|--------|------|
| Link-type weights in related / recommended queries    |      | x   |        |      |
|-------------------------------------------------------|------|-----|--------|------|
| Batch updates support in exporter                     | X    | x   | x      |      |
|-------------------------------------------------------|------|-----|--------|------|
| Support for grabbing properties in related query      | X    |     |        |      |
|-------------------------------------------------------|------|-----|--------|------|
